<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Confirmation - {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e, #16a34a);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .checkmark {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #22c55e;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 30px;
        }
        .application-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .value {
            color: #6b7280;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #22c55e;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 10px 0;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #16a34a;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #22c55e;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            color: #d97706;
        }
        .motivation-section {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        }
        .motivation-text {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .motivation-quote {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-left: 3px solid #0ea5e9;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
        }
        .warning-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .warning-box h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #d97706;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                width: auto;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .value {
                margin-top: 5px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="cid:company-logo" alt="{{companyName}}" class="logo">
            <h1>Application Received Successfully!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for your interest in becoming our dealership partner</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="success-icon">
                <div class="checkmark">‚úì</div>
            </div>
            
            <h2>Dear {{fullName}},</h2>
            
            <p>We have successfully received your dealership application. Thank you for your interest in partnering with us to promote sustainable transportation solutions!</p>
            
            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>Application Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Application ID:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{applicationId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Submission Date:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{submissionDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Status:</span>
                    <span class="value"><span class="status-badge">Under Review</span></span>
                </div>
                <!-- Personal Details -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Full Name:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{fullName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{email}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Phone Number:</span>
                    <span class="value">+91 {{phoneNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Age:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{age}} years</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Business Details -->
                {{#if businessName}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Business Name:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{businessName}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Business Type:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{businessType}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if gstNumber}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">GST Number:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{gstNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Automotive Experience:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{hasExperience}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if experienceDetails}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Experience Details:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{experienceDetails}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <!-- Location Details -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Location:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{city}}, {{state}} - {{pincode}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Area Type:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{areaType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Dealership Address:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{dealershipAddress}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Property Status:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{propertyStatus}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Infrastructure -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Showroom Size:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{showroomSize}} sq. ft.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Service Area:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{hasServiceArea}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Parking Space:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{hasParkingSpace}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Power Backup:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{hasPowerBackup}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Charging Station:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{hasChargingStation}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Investment & Financials -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Investment Capacity:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{investmentCapacity}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Investment Source:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{investmentSource}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Willing to Meet Targets:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{meetTargets}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Team Setup -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Planned Sales Executives:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{salesExecutives}} person(s)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Planned Technicians:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{technicians}} person(s)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Willing to Train Staff:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{trainStaff}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Brand Exclusivity -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Brand Exclusivity:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{exclusivity}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Documents -->
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Documents Submitted:</span>
                    <span class="value">
                        {{#if idProof}}ID Proof, {{/if}}
                        {{#if addressProof}}Address Proof, {{/if}}
                        {{#if businessProof}}Business Proof, {{/if}}
                        {{#if propertyLayout}}Property Layout{{/if}}
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>üöÄ What Happens Next?</h3>
                <p><strong>Review Process (5-7 business days):</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Our team will review your application and supporting documents</li>
                    <li>We may contact you for additional information if needed</li>
                    <li>Background and business verification will be conducted</li>
                </ul>
                
                <p><strong>Decision & Onboarding:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>You'll receive an email with our decision within 7 business days</li>
                    <li>If approved, we'll schedule an onboarding call to discuss next steps</li>
                    <li>Training materials and dealership agreement will be provided</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="motivation-section">
                <h3>üí° Your Motivation</h3>
                <div class="motivation-text">
                    <p><strong>Why do you want this dealership?</strong></p>
                    <p class="motivation-quote">"{{motivation}}"</p>
                </div>
            </div>
                <h4>üìû Need Assistance?</h4>
                <p>If you have any questions about your application, please don't hesitate to reach out:</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> partnerships@{{companyDomain}}<br>
                <strong>Phone:</strong> {{supportPhone}}<br>
                <strong>Business Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday, 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM</p>
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Note</h4>
                <p>Please save this email for your records. Your application ID <strong>{{applicationId}}</strong> will be required for any future correspondence regarding this application.</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="cta-button">Track Application Status</a>
            </div>

            <p>We appreciate your interest in joining our network of dealership partners and look forward to potentially working together to expand sustainable transportation solutions.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>{{companyName}} Partnership Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="{{websiteUrl}}">Website</a>
                <a href="{{facebookUrl}}">Facebook</a>
                <a href="{{twitterUrl}}">Twitter</a>
                <a href="{{linkedinUrl}}">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>¬© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>{{companyAddress}}</p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
                This email was sent to {{email}}. If you believe you received this email in error, 
                please contact our support team at support@{{companyDomain}}.
            </p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af;">
                Please do not reply to this email as it is sent from an unmonitored address. 
                For support, use the contact information provided above.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>